nk ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/upcoming-tata-cars-in-india\/#Tata_Tiago_EV\" title=\"Tata Tiago EV\">Tata Tiago EV<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/upcoming-tata-cars-in-india\/#Tata_Altroz_XT_Dark_Edition\" title=\"Tata Altroz XT Dark Edition\">Tata Altroz XT Dark Edition<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/upcoming-tata-cars-in-india\/#Tata_Sierra\" title=\"Tata Sierra\">Tata Sierra<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/upcoming-tata-cars-in-india\/#Final_Words\" title=\"Final Words\">Final Words<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Why_Tata_cars\"><\/span>Why Tata cars?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Tata cars are safer as compared to other cars. Tata is India&#x2019;s first-ever car to have a 5-star global NCAP rating. Tata also has a comparatively cheaper car. The cheapest car in India is Tata Nano, which is priced around 1 lakh. Talking about comfort, the new generation Tata cars are pretty comfortable and luxurious. The engines used by Tata cars are very powerful. Most importantly Tata is a 100% Indian brand. So, if you believe in vocal for local, then why not buy a car which profits the country in the long run.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tata_Kite_5\"><\/span>Tata Kite 5<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1700 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/tata-kite-5-e1647929244756.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"274\" height=\"155\" \/><\/p>\n<p>If you are in search of a sedan for your compact family, then here&#x2019;s the right choice. In a 2016 Auto Expo, Tata introduced this compact sedan. With an ARAI mileage of 17.1kmpl and engine displacement of 1198cc, the car produces a power of 84bhp and a torque of 114Nm. The car has a sporty styling exterior, an integrated spoiler with a LED stop lamp, and 15-inch wheels. The car is equipped with a Harman-powered infotainment system, paired with an 8 speaker sound system. It&#x2019;s a highly fuel-efficient car that delivers around 20kmpl in its petrol version. Some features that will sway your heart away include a large air intake, tapering roof-line, prominent window lines, anti locking braking system, new electric power steering, and spacious cabins for your luxurious comfort. The model also has basic safety features like dual air bags and ABS. With an estimated price of 4.5 lakhs, Tata Kite 5 is the cheapest sedan to be launched in India. This car comes under the title of the most budget-friendly car that you can purchase in 2022. The expected launch date of Kite 5 is yet to be announced.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tata_Altroz_EV\"><\/span>Tata Altroz EV<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1701 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/tata-altroz-ev.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"259\" height=\"193\" \/><\/p>\n<p>If you want to buy a Tata car this summer, then your hustle is over, because Tata is launching its new Tata Altroz EV in June 2022. Tata unveiled the new Altroz EV at the Auto Expo 2020. With the great success of Tata Altroz, Tata is all set to launch its EV. This EV draws its power from IP67 rated dust and water proof battery that can cover a distance of up to 300km on a single charge. This premium electric hatchback has a seating capacity of 5 and offers its customers only a single color accounting for teal blue. It is available in automatic transmission and electric options. They are approximately the same as Altroz, but only a change is present in the gear box, which automatically increases the space inside the car. The exterior of the car accounts for a redesigned air dam, new grille, and electric blue accents. The Altroz EV has an estimated price range between 12 to 15 lakhs. If you are in search of an EV then the best mid-range car option is to buy the new Tata Altroz EV and make your drives hassle free.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tata_Tiago_EV\"><\/span>Tata Tiago EV<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1702 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/tata-tiago-ev.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"276\" height=\"183\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Tata is all ready to launch a new model of the <a href=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/upcoming-electric-cars-in-india-2022\/\">electric car<\/a>, mainly, Tata Tiago EV, in March 2022. It is expected to provide a range of about 306km in a single charge. The car is inspired by its standard model. This hatchback will provide its customers only a single color, mainly white. If you want to buy a Tata EV, but your pocket does not allow you to buy one, then here is the right choice for you. The Tata Tiago comes with a pocket friendly budget and is expected to have a price range between 5 lakh to 7 lakh. A perfect hatchback for your nuclear families, to wander all around the city, is available in Automatic Transmission and Electric Range options. This EV is identical to its petrol version, in all its luxuries and comfort. The Tiago EV is powered by a 30kW electric motor that produces the electricity to cover large miles.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tata_Altroz_XT_Dark_Edition\"><\/span>Tata Altroz XT Dark Edition<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1703 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Tata-Altroz-XT-Dark-Edition.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"276\" height=\"183\" \/><\/p>\n<p>With its new launch in May 2022, Tata is back with its another hatchback, the Tata Altroz XT Dark Edition. This car provides an ARAI mileage of 19.05kmpl and engine displacement of 1199cc, which produces a maximum power of 84.88bhp at 600rpm and a torque of around 113Nm at 3300rpm. The key features of this dark edition include power windows front, automatic climate control, power adjustable exterior rear view mirror, wheel covers, and engine start stop button. In terms of safety, Tata ensures you with all the safety features that include, passenger airbags, anti lock braking system, front fog lights, and driver airbags. With additional safety features such as a tire pressure monitoring system and a brake sway control, Tata always surprises its customers and makes it the <a href=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/safest-cars-in-india-2022\/%20\">safest car<\/a>. This hatchback is estimated at around 7.9 lakhs.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tata_Sierra\"><\/span>Tata Sierra<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-1704 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/tata-sierra-300x171.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"171\" srcset=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/tata-sierra-300x171.webp 300w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/tata-sierra.webp 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Last but not the least, Tata unveiled the Sierra at the Auto Expo 2020. The company is still accessing the feasibility of the model, henceforth the launch date is yet to be announced. This is another compact SUV from Tata that is going to be launched in the near future. This model is all set to bring back the iconic nameplate in the new avatar, which is greener. This new electric car is based on the ALFA ARC platform and features LED headlamps, black cladding at the bottom edge, and dual-tone alloy wheels. With a seating capacity of 5, the car can cover a distance of up to 400km on a single charge. The estimated price of the new Tata Sierra is approximately 14 lakhs, as expected before its launch. This SUV is designed on the concept of Tata&#x2019;s IMPACT 2.0 design language.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Final_Words\"><\/span>Final Words<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>After reading the entire article, still, are you making up your mind to buy a Tata car? Tata has always pleased its customers with its impeccable design and comfort features. Then why not set the alert notifications for the launch of these cars and buy the one which suits your needs and finances at the best. Vehicle care is always ready to bring its handpicked collection of the best cars for you all in different categories. Make full use of this article and pre-book your favorite Tata car now.<\/p>\n<p>Ride Safe || Ride Happily.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Maintaining a legacy of 75 years, Tata has gained dominant supremacy in the automobile industry. For years, Tata is known to make sturdy and robust cars in the industry that always steals its customers&#x2019;&#46;&#46;&#46;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":200024,"featured_media":1722,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[71],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1691"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\